---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`Product Solutions - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="We specialize in certified secure hardware and communication solutions for enterprise and government requirements." />

<Header />
<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Product Solutions</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Certified Security Hardware & Communications</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="products-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro">
				<p>We specialize in identifying and providing certified security products that meet stringent government and enterprise requirements. Our focus is on solutions that align with international standards and New Zealand security frameworks.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="product-categories">
				<section class="category">
					<h2>Encrypted Storage Solutions</h2>
					<p>Hardware-encrypted storage devices that protect data at rest with certified encryption standards.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>FIPS 140-2 validated encryption</li>
						<li>Hardware-based AES-256 bit encryption</li>
						<li>PIN-authenticated access controls</li>
						<li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Product Evaluation Phase:</strong> We are currently evaluating certified encrypted USB and storage solutions for our portfolio.
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="category">
					<h2>Secure Communication Devices</h2>
					<p>Certified encrypted communication platforms for enterprise and specialized environments.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>End-to-end encrypted messaging</li>
						<li>Secure voice and video communication</li>
						<li>Commercial-grade encryption solutions</li>
						<li>Compliance with data protection standards</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Market Research:</strong> Researching certified communication solutions that meet our security standards.
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="category">
					<h2>Access Control & Authentication</h2>
					<p>Multi-factor authentication and secure access solutions for sensitive environments.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Hardware security tokens</li>
						<li>Multi-factor authentication devices</li>
						<li>Biometric authentication solutions</li>
						<li>Physical access control systems</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Vendor Selection:</strong> Assessing authentication solutions for enterprise deployment.
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>

			<section class="partner-cta">
				<h2>For Product Manufacturers & Distributors</h2>
				<p>Are you a manufacturer of certified security products? We are seeking partnership opportunities with companies offering:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>FIPS 140-2 certified encryption products</li>
					<li>NLNCSA DEP-V & NATO Restricted certified solutions</li>
					<li>NZISM-aligned security hardware</li>
					<li>Enterprise-grade secure communication devices</li>
				</ul>
				<p>We are building our product portfolio and welcome discussions with qualified manufacturers and distributors.</p>
				<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz?subject=Product Partnership Inquiry" class="btn primary">Discuss Partnership</a>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>

</main>
<Footer />

<style>
body {
	margin: 0;
	min-height: 100vh;
	font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
	line-height: 1.6;
	background: #f8fafc;
}

main {
	flex: 1;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
	padding: 6rem 2rem;
	text-align: center;
	background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1419 0%, #1a365d 50%, #2d3748 100%);
	color: white;
	position: relative;
	overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
	content: "";
	position: absolute;
	top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
	background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg width="100%25" height="100%25" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle fill="%2363b3ed" fill-opacity="0.05" cx="10%25" cy="20%25" r="80"/><circle fill="%2363b3ed" fill-opacity="0.03" cx="80%25" cy="70%25" r="120"/><circle fill="%2390cdf4" fill-opacity="0.04" cx="50%25" cy="50%25" r="100"/></svg>');
	z-index: 0;
}
.hero > .container {
	position: relative;
	z-index: 1;
}
.hero h1 {
	font-size: 4rem;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: 900;
	color: #ffffff;
	text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 2px 0 #1a365d;
	letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
.tagline {
	font-size: 1.8rem;
	font-weight: 400;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	color: #90cdf4;
}

/* Products Content */
.products-content {
	padding: 5rem 1rem;
	background: #f8fafc;
}
.intro {
	text-align: center;
	max-width: 900px;
	margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	font-size: 1.15rem;
	line-height: 1.7;
}
.product-categories {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
	gap: 2rem;
	max-width: 1200px;
	margin: 0 auto 4rem;
}
.category {
	background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0f4f8 100%);
	padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
	border-radius: 0.75rem;
	border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
	box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,54,93,0.12), 0 1.5px 4px rgba(26,54,93,0.07);
	transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: flex-start;
}
.category:hover {
	box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(26,54,93,0.16);
	transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.01);
}
.category h2 {
	color: #0f1419;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: 600;
	letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
.category ul {
	margin: 1rem 0;
	padding-left: 1.5rem;
}
.category li {
	margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	line-height: 1.6;
}
.status-note {
	background: #f0f4f8;
	border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
	border-left: 4px solid #3182ce;
	padding: 1rem;
	border-radius: 0.5rem;
	margin-top: 1.5rem;
	font-size: 0.95rem;
	color: #2d3748;
}

/* Partner CTA */
.partner-cta {
	background: #0f1419;
	color: white;
	padding: 4rem 3rem;
	border-radius: 0.75rem;
	max-width: 900px;
	margin: 0 auto;
	text-align: center;
	box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,54,93,0.12), 0 1.5px 4px rgba(26,54,93,0.07);
	border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
	transition: all 0.3s ease;
	position: relative;
}
.partner-cta:hover {
	transform: translateY(-5px);
	box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(26,54,93,0.18), 0 4px 12px rgba(26,54,93,0.15);
}
.partner-cta h2 {
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	color: #90cdf4;
	font-size: 2.2rem;
	font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: 700;
	letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.partner-cta ul {
	text-align: left;
	max-width: 600px;
	margin: 1.5rem auto;
}
.partner-cta li {
	margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	line-height: 1.6;
}
.btn, .btn.primary {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  background-color: #90cdf4;
  color: #1a365d;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26,54,93,0.07);
  font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
.btn:hover, .btn.primary:hover {
  background-color: #63b3ed;
  color: #1a365d;
}
.btn:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
}
.container {
	max-width: 1200px;
	margin: 0 auto;
	text-align: center;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .products-content {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }
  .category {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .partner-cta {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }
  .partner-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .hero {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .category h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .category {
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
  }
  .partner-cta {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }
  .partner-cta h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }
  .btn {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .product-categories {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 98vw;
  }
  .category {
    max-width: 100%;
  }
}
</style>
